Requirements:
SPN: Service Principal Name
To establish connection between AZURE devops and azure portal.

Tabs:
Pipeline: Click on Add to Build the pipeline to add artifacts
Continuous deployment trigger: For continuous deployment when ever there is a build
Add stages (SIT, UAT, PRODUCTION)
Stages consists of Pre-deployment conditions and Post deployment conditions
Pre-deployment conditions:
After-release
After-stage
Manual
2. Artifacts filter:
To select one or more artifacts
3. Pull request deployment
4. Pre-deployment approval
5. Gates

Post Deployment Conditions:
Auto redeploy trigger: To deploy last successful deployment incase the present deployment is failed. 

